@startuml S5 - Upload Tugas

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam maxmessagesize 100
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ArrowColor #000000
skinparam BorderColor #000000
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #000000
skinparam ParticipantFontColor #000000
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActorBorderColor #000000
skinparam ActorFontColor #000000
skinparam DatabaseBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam DatabaseBorderColor #000000
skinparam DatabaseFontColor #000000
skinparam BoxBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam BoxBorderColor #000000
skinparam BoxFontColor #000000
skinparam LifeLineBorderColor #000000
skinparam LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam NoteBorderColor #000000
skinparam NoteFontColor #000000

actor Mahasiswa
actor Dosen
participant "S5. Upload Tugas" as UploadTugas
participant "Multer (File Handler)" as Multer
database "DS2: Tugas (PengumpulanTugas)" as DBTugas

== Mahasiswa Upload Tugas ==

Mahasiswa -> UploadTugas : Pilih file jawaban + isi catatan
UploadTugas -> Multer : Proses upload file
Multer -> Multer : Validasi tipe & ukuran file
Multer --> UploadTugas : Path file tersimpan di /uploads/

alt Sudah pernah mengumpulkan
    UploadTugas -> DBTugas : Update PengumpulanTugas (fileJawaban baru)
    DBTugas --> UploadTugas : Data pengumpulan diperbarui
else Belum pernah mengumpulkan
    UploadTugas -> DBTugas : Insert PengumpulanTugas baru
    DBTugas --> UploadTugas : Data pengumpulan tersimpan
end

UploadTugas --> Mahasiswa : Konfirmasi tugas berhasil dikumpulkan
UploadTugas --> Mahasiswa : Tampilkan nama file sebelumnya sebagai link biru

== Mahasiswa Lihat Status Pengumpulan ==

Mahasiswa -> UploadTugas : Buka halaman pengumpulan tugas
UploadTugas -> DBTugas : Cek PengumpulanTugas by idTugas + NIM
DBTugas --> UploadTugas : Data submission (fileJawaban, catatan)
UploadTugas --> Mahasiswa : Tampilkan file sebelumnya + status sudah kumpul

== Dosen Menerima Tugas Mahasiswa ==

Dosen -> UploadTugas : Lihat pengumpulan per tugas
UploadTugas -> DBTugas : Ambil semua PengumpulanTugas by idTugas
DBTugas --> UploadTugas : List mahasiswa + status + fileJawaban
UploadTugas --> Dosen : Tampilkan daftar mahasiswa yang sudah/belum kumpul

@enduml
